Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為早河那傢伙的這次一定玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始之樹引起的騷亂剛結束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次絕園魔法使又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來 對魔法最瞭解的還是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是國內 國外也在催我們盡快找出對策
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕園魔法使簡直就像是為了讓早河復任才出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:02:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕園魔法使的出現真是值得慶幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他的出現 各國開始正式對樹展開了調查研究
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我指的是對你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心裡到底在謀劃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是穩定事態而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩樹關係著文明的存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能穩定這一事態的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織裡除了我別無他人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個 就不擇手段嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國聯希望得到關於樹的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要得罪他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年在你的指揮下 對策軍被派出之後全軍覆沒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以為你已經擺脫責任了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 降職並不能擺脫我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會公開我掌握的所有信息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也會秘密動用內閣秘密搜索室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:03:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話 你會死得很慘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭然於心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:05.68,每集標題,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,501)}海雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！ 堅果！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新加坡也在賣啊 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在巴塞羅那也買了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了羽村 兩個星期就幾乎環遊了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽村也吃堅果就好了嘛 堅果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,營養豐富嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那個看上去像樹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因人而異吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹被奉為神靈也不稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日耳曼神話的依格德拉西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.69,每集標題-furigana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(593,43)}依格德拉西爾：宇宙生命大梣樹，象徵天上、人間、地獄和宇宙間一切有生命之物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基督教的生命之樹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然大家都輕易接受了那大樹的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不如說那更像是疑似大樹的某物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才接近其本質
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有網友和研究者說那是蛇或龍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇或龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 而且蛇和龍也經常被當做神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 羽村才一會兒就變身英雄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多看出左門他們在想什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始之樹吸收了軍隊的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將一切生物變為金屬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不能與之對抗 除了接受別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累積的不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人般英雄人物的登場恰逢時宜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對始之樹抱有反感和疑問的人差不多也要起來反抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好可以借勢利用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 好好吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊考慮事情邊吃飯可不利於消化哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 細嚼慢咽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大中午的就共進軟綿綿的蛋包飯 還相視而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是在約會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須對吉野死心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微和他多待一會 就更加喜歡他了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是吉野為什麼沒注意到我喜歡他的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在富士山的推理那麼完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有女朋友的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該對女孩子的心思很敏感才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了真正喜歡的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的女孩就無法入眼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 男人就應該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真那麼風流多情 我也會主動謝絕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 又發現了一個吉野的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去不是越發喜歡他了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底要怎樣才能對吉野死心？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕緊斬斷情絲的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡那若隱若現的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總盼著吉野的女朋友能消失的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被始之樹汲取後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好有朝一日真的會害了他女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉風 要喝點什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有沒有汽水啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.59,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうだ（對了）和ソーダ（汽水）發音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你女朋友是個怎樣的姑娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了 快告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那姑娘是長得比我好看呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是性格比我好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是腦袋比我聰明？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪種？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然這樣問我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼就沒注意到啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能配得上吉野這種男生的姑娘一定比我更優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能詳細瞭解她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能用「無法趕超」這個念頭讓自己死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女朋友長得非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 這個是你親手做的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是故意裝成像親手做的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天才第一次知道「隔水煮」這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 要是市面上賣的我也能放心吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 情人節能和女朋友一起賞雪吃巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好特別的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然除我之外 又收了這麼女孩的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友送的又哪裡特別了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒生氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是自己的男朋友被嫌棄到一個巧克力都收不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才困擾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在深海中落下的皚皚白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨大海的永存而永不停息飄落的雪花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在水中 飄下的速度也慢了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就彷彿時間的流逝只在那才變得平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不也一樣會有點那種感覺麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我們倆乘坐的深海潛艇裡 也飄進幾朵海雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海雪 實際上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本是由浮游生物的粉狀遺骸粘結而成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的雪也可能是什麼來歷不明的物體的殘骸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 雪不就是普通的冰的結晶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣裡也有廢氣 工廠煤煙等大氣污染物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附著昆蟲殘骸的可能性也很高…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你還是因為我收到別人的巧克力生氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是個學富五車想像力豐富的女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 只是喜歡挖苦性格又差罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是有點糟糕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們孤男寡女地出去旅行了這麼多星期
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被你那喜歡挖苦的女朋友知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會火冒三丈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這麼肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是個男人連手指頭都不願碰的恐龍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你女朋友才完全不擔心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉風？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是你想說我比你女朋友的性格還惡劣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉風你又是美女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且跟我女朋友比起來性格方面完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美女…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 暑假的時候我和她有過這樣的對話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班裡的同學叫我把吉野介紹給大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我就陰沉著臉說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙看似純良實際是個極惡非道的人格缺失者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是介紹給你們 到時發生什麼事我可不負責
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是大家也不知為什麼就謝絕說「那就不用介紹了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正介紹了也不會有什麼結果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如讓她們早點死了這份心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？ 也有可能意外地進展順利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若果真如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個刨冰機現在磨的就不是冰而是吉野你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把你放到業務冷凍櫃裡凍得硬邦邦的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再小心翼翼地把你磨碎掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來不像是開玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我就沒在開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要移情於其他女孩子也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對人肉刨冰還是蠻有興趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過應該不會有這麼一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我只能和吉野交往一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野也只能和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我滿腦子想的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野你可有膽子敢背叛這樣的我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以後我就很少跟她提其他女生的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我感覺到 果然她的身邊只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不單單是所謂喜歡或討厭的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是非常確信 她很需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也一樣很需要你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很需要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我不能這麼想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽村好像回日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好像在煩惱不適應時差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了羽村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個世界開始重新思考始之樹了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼剩下的就只有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕園之樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 絕園魔法使之心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:37.77,副本sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(183,212)}新宿ALTA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:37.77,副本sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1060,232)}始之樹到底是什麼？\N 各地開始爭論
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於始之樹 世界變得和平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:37.76,最後問題,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(928,407)}日本再生會\N小笠原會長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然環境和治安都令人吃驚地改…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:46.96,Copy of Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(258,193)}因絕園魔法使而\N騷動的日本列島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:46.96,Copy of Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1031,438)}激烈爭論 對熱情高漲的律師\N芝千春跟蹤採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕園魔法使是我們的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能接受始之樹的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:52.09,Copy of Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1015,450)}究竟會怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:52.09,Copy of Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1010,489)}始之樹vs絕園魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始之樹絕對是支配者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕園魔法使才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情都搞這麼大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很痛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你的腸胃很弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個身體都要裂開了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等吉野的聯絡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個 在懷疑吉野是絕園魔法使吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕園魔法使除了我還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你要是魔法使才奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算能靈活使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻一點也沒有殺人之心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然發現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕園魔法使的身心會不會分離了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身心？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以往發生的事來看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀧川吉野是絕園魔法使的嫌疑很高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了和擁有絕對力量的始之樹對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕園之樹為了保護他 而將心從身體分離
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不會使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:14:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但擅長謀略 並擁有絕園之心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是吉野嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這還只是揣測
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果吉野是絕園魔法使的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份謀略未免太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓葉風懷有愛戀之心 從某種意義上說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和將始之樹的加護據為己有一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我能不能殺了吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也包含了這可能性嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果瀧川吉野是絕園魔法使的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是他殺了你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有必要殺了吉野的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會借你一臂之力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先搞清楚吉野女朋友的身份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今吉野也沒有告訴任何人他女朋友的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因為她是最能影響他的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成為不錯的人質
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下是在包庇瀧川吉野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘀咕什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:14:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她成最後的王牌了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果吉野是絕園魔法使的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在重要時刻也會拋棄她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時殺了他就行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此沒用的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他活著也沒什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們來推測一下誰是吉野的女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 什麼時候都能跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…對啊 嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉風？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:44.08,標題,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,370)}吉野的女朋友會議
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中時期的女朋友應該是同校的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算擴大範圍最多也就是附近的女中學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他平時有和誰接觸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個依據可能有點微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好幾次都想給他介紹女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:15:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於吉野腹黑的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近所有的女生都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不是那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠言有時比真相更可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想幫他找女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真廣 你也會被當成他的同夥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹可真嚴厲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說瀧川吉野的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不被謠言所困 看清吉野本質的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:33.14,標題-furigana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,286)}看透真相的眼睛（重要）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…為什麼需要白板？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要記錄人員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記錄人員…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越聽越覺得吉野的女朋友是個麻煩的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野卻深深迷戀著她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是苦戀還是癡迷 快說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為公主的我卻煩惱於戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還關係著世界的走向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？ 戀愛喜劇嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上整個世界命運的戀愛喜劇嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對最親密的真廣也隱瞞了女友 不是很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就應該有充分的理由才隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說愧於被知道身份的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校的女教師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就算是對最好的朋友也難以啟齒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世俗說法上過不去 所以才隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者 有夫之婦如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和吉野沒認識什麼有夫之婦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 不是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼胸部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是個胸部過大的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕別人知道自己的性癖好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說正好相反？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有比自己年齡小的可能嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙喜歡比自己年長的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是為了擾亂視聽才這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果女朋友是小學生左右的年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是很難啟齒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:15.32,標題,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(611,64)}女教師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:16.20,標題,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(569,62)}人妻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.35,標題,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(578,81)}胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:18.31,標題,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(675,66)}蘿莉控
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些…有必要都寫出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽村 你有什麼想說的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 會不會是食堂的大嬸？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我認真點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們憑什麼說我？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能使出殺手鐧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海雪…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我沒生氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不太信…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣站在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有種會永遠和吉野在一起的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很冷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想一直都這樣站著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又說多餘的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聯繫女朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅是「好感」的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是被稱為「戀愛」最高級別的那種心跳不止的喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在也很想擁抱你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想摸摸你的耳垂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸耳垂？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是讓人著急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個被始之樹所護佑的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為始之公主的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把你據為己有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有女朋友這件事讓我很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.99,0:20:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至會想這世上要沒有她該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最可怕的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始之樹察覺到了我的這份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會為了我殺掉你女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進而徹底除掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒辦法控制好自己的感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以吉野 趕緊讓我對你死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是蘿莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護士怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家為什麼要故意排除那個可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.10,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護士太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:09.78,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不小
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:11.75,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是空姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能說句話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.03,0:21:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要說女朋友的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我所聞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野的女朋友只可能是那個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近你是因為這個才變得這麼奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 我還是別再隱瞞比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.68,0:21:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心我女朋友的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正始之樹也拿她也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你隨便說出這麼不合理的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒法安心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是合理的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛奧菲莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有千萬兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們全部的愛聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.37,0:22:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也抵不上我一個人的這份愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對在一年前就已經死去的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有必要這麼惴惴不安嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.69,0:22:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野的女朋友會不會是真廣的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不破愛花
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁閉？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.22,0:24:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 把我打倒 羽村
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.29,0:24:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼公主殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是在不該動搖的時候動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼劇情發展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.59,0:24:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.50,0:24:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本無法預想之後的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.26,0:24:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全預想不到
